baseline: We compared changes in mental_health functioning over 18months for children who remained in-home with parent training versus those placed in stable OOH care.
high_intensity: We compared significant changes in mental_health functioning over 18 months for children who remained in-home with intensive parent training versus those placed in stable OOH care.
low_intensity: We compared minor changes in mental_health functioning over 18 months for children who remained in-home with basic parent training versus those placed in stable OOH care.

baseline: Among those with general mental_health problems, 29.5 sought professional help.
high_intensity: Among those with severe mental_health issues, 29.5 urgently sought professional help.
low_intensity: Among those with mild mental_health concerns, 29.5 casually sought professional help.

baseline: However, this approach has yet to be evaluated in athletes who are interested in optimizing their mental_health and sport performance, but have no indication of pathology.
high_intensity: However, this promising approach has yet to be rigorously evaluated in athletes who are deeply interested in optimizing their mental_health and sport performance, but have no indication of severe pathology.
low_intensity: However, this approach has yet to be casually evaluated in athletes who are somewhat interested in optimizing their mental_health and sport performance, but have no indication of any significant issues.

baseline: Many service members in need of mental_health treatment do not seek such treatment.
high_intensity: Many service members in desperate need of urgent mental_health treatment do not seek such vital treatment.
low_intensity: Many service members in need of some mental_health support do not seek such treatment.

baseline: CSET within the context of significant other support is important to consider in understanding firefighter mental_health.
high_intensity: CSET within the context of significant other support is crucial to consider in comprehensively understanding deteriorating firefighter mental_health.
